HEADWORD: Gowany
<hw>Gow"an*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having, abounding in,
or decked with, daisies.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sweeter than <qex>gowany</qex> glens or new-mown hay.</q>
<rj><qau>Ramsay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gowd</ent>⟦br⟧
